### KYC Verification — KycVerificationAgent
### POST /api/kyc/verify
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Low-risk case: straightforward clean customer → direct APPROVE path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kyc/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST-001",
  "fullName": "Anna Müller",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-03-12",
  "nationality": "German",
  "occupation": "Software Engineer",
  "sourceOfFunds": "Salary"
}

###

### High-risk case: PEP match → enhanced due diligence path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kyc/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST-002",
  "fullName": "Viktor Petrov",
  "dateOfBirth": "1972-11-05",
  "nationality": "Russian",
  "occupation": "Government Official",
  "sourceOfFunds": "Government salary and real estate"
}

###

### Edge case: optional fields omitted — occupation and sourceOfFunds are null
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kyc/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST-003",
  "fullName": "Maria Santos",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-07-22",
  "nationality": "Brazilian",
  "occupation": null,
  "sourceOfFunds": null
}

###

### Edge case: high-risk nationality with adverse media signal
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kyc/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST-004",
  "fullName": "Kim Jin-ho",
  "dateOfBirth": "1968-04-15",
  "nationality": "North Korean",
  "occupation": "Private Investor",
  "sourceOfFunds": "Unknown"
}

###

### Edge case: max-field customer — all fields provided
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kyc/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST-005",
  "fullName": "François Dupont",
  "dateOfBirth": "1979-12-01",
  "nationality": "French",
  "occupation": "Hedge Fund Manager",
  "sourceOfFunds": "Investment returns, dividends, and carried interest from private equity"
}
